00:05:36.760 --> 00:05:42.200
being a part of an organization as a data science team or a data science leader,

00:05:42.200 --> 00:05:49.160
or a data leader, or whatever, isn't about algorithms or data science in that sense,

00:05:49.160 --> 00:05:56.600
or cool structures, or cool inference methods. It's about seeing where you can bring value

