up my fantastic team spirit and belonging to something bigger than yourself. First off,

00:15:53.880 --> 00:16:02.440
I'd like to emphasize the importance of being agile in your development. And I'm not saying

00:16:02.440 --> 00:16:12.599
that because Agile is cool or the main thing I take from an Agile approach is that you have

00:16:12.599 --> 00:16:20.280
dailies and you have opportunities to set these and take these big goals. Like you want to run

00:16:20.280 --> 00:16:29.080
a marathon, but you're going to break it into pieces. And when you do that, you realize that,

00:16:29.080 --> 00:16:36.039
hey, this overall big goal is not something that I need to think about all the time. I only think

00:16:36.039 --> 00:16:43.719
