00:16:43.719 --> 00:16:51.640
celebrate with your team. And then you get this positive feedback that, hey, I did something

00:16:51.640 --> 00:16:58.440
important. I didn't complete this whole marathon, but we've reached our short sighted goal or like

00:16:58.440 --> 00:17:07.000
short term goals. And on daily or planning, I share that with my team and got this positive

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:14.280
feedback that, hey, I did well. If I didn't, you know, break this goal into pieces, you're losing

00:17:14.280 --> 00:17:22.119
