idea? I can't, I'm not sure. I know I have done it over the years and I have learned this the hard

00:49:04.679 --> 00:49:14.360
way. So I have a story to share when I was at the bank. And so we were trying to push the boundaries

00:49:15.159 --> 00:49:21.560
there. Like we were trying to incorporate data science into many aspects of the operations of

00:49:21.560 --> 00:49:29.479
the bank. And I remember quite distinctly this meeting I had with the corporate department.

00:49:29.479 --> 00:49:36.360
And what we're trying to, I was building a model that can help them quantify and categorize

